<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA25">
<l>ceṉṟa tilaṅkaimēṟ cevvētaṉ cīṟṟattāṟ</l>
<l>koṉṟa tirāvaṇaṉaik kūṟuṅkā – ṉiṉṟatuvum</l>
<l>vēyōṅku taṇcāral vēṅkaṭamē viṇṇavartam</l>
<l>vāyōṅku tolpukaḻāṉ vantu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He came [and] went straight to Laṅkā, killed Rāvaṇa</l>
<l>with his anger, when one talks about it, and he stands</l>
<l>on Vēṅkaṭam with cool slopes high with bamboo, the one</l>
<l>of high ancient praise in the mouth of the celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
